div.p:
These components are divided by: 
  Priority, that means how urgent they are; 
  Type, which include new model components to configure in the Atlantis framework (socio-economic components) and data which can be composed of single data or time series; 
  Periodicity, correspond the ideal maximum time lag needed for the information; and 
  Spatial if the information that is needed should be at the spatial level. Note that information at the level of the species should primary include key species from the ecosystem such as Spiny lobster, J.F. morwong, sea urchins.
